Acqua Point brings all like-minded people who drink water on one platform and encourages them to refill their water bottles instead of purchasing bottled water.
The objective of the app is to eliminate plastic wastage which is causing tremendous pollution to the planet earth.  
 
The App  has an interface with two options - Provider and Collector. Anyone can enrol as a Provider or a Collector using the App. The App connects these two using 
the Google maps API based on the nearest point.  
